data.description: Beautiful 3 bed 3.5 bath farm house is a convenient location. The hardwood floors run throughout much of the open concept floor plan. All 3 bedrooms boast there own baths. The master bedroom will feel like a true retreat, upstairs with three closets, a bathroom complete with a double vanity and jetted bathtub. The outdoor space offers something for everyone! There are 4 outbuildings - 2 of them measure 40x60 and a third measures 40x70. With a 6.6 acre property bordering brand new development, the options are vast!
